\begin_layout Standard
No one was worried at first.
 Hook goblins were ferocious and very deadly if one allowed them to get close,
 but they weren't particularly tough and went down easily before concentrated
 spellfire.
 Indeed, the first wave was nothing special, lulling the Ibasan defenders into
 a false sense of safety.
 But as they killed one wave of hook goblins, then two, and then 

\emph on

